text: Dmitry Jakovenko (born 29 June 1983) is a Russian chess grandmaster. On the July 2009 FIDE rating list, Jakovenko had a rating of 2760, but he has slipped a bit since then. He shared first in the Russian Championship 2006, losing the playoff against Evgeny Alekseev. Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Russian chess players Category:Chess grandmasters
